{"tid":1388392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"維基百科有冇呢兩個月每一場既條目？","createTime":"2019-07-30T16:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:24:16.000Z","uid":77547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"742c96b86e33dd893a4d652e9ba79efc6482d66f","tid":1388392,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:41:47.000Z","msg":"或者時序？好奇一問。因為太多場都就嚟一次過記唔曬"},{"pid":"3ddef7a6860f2ae2fee8b96600005c282a8b6a07","tid":1388392,"uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:48:21.000Z","msg":"其實有，但有好多內容細節位（好似727元朗清場、728中西區衝突），又或者比較細嘅行動（去九龍灣港鐵總部示威、44部公務員加入聯署）都miss 咗冇人更新同理會。<br />\n<br />\n而且本身靠幾丁友去編輯，咁多事件都未必follow 得切。以往寫開果班完全潛哂水賴政治潔癖，一係就改小小野就算。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過最大問題係好多事件條目都冇「自由圖片」。</span>維基百科規定媒體作品一定要作商業用途同容許任何修改。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n但其他民間媒體（好似獨媒、Socrec)又唔肯將d相商業用其實好難搞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTemplate%3A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=6e56e0e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0</a>"},{"pid":"a6416c1638debdf5aad1d5dc3be7135baf29b5d4","tid":1388392,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ddef7a6860f2ae2fee8b96600005c282a8b6a07","tid":1388392,"uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:48:21.000Z","msg":"其實有，但有好多內容細節位（好似727元朗清場、728中西區衝突），又或者比較細嘅行動（去九龍灣港鐵總部示威、44部公務員加入聯署）都miss 咗冇人更新同理會。<br />\n<br />\n而且本身靠幾丁友去編輯，咁多事件都未必follow 得切。以往寫開果班完全潛哂水賴政治潔癖，一係就改小小野就算。<br />\n<br /